{
  "texts": [
    "The physiological conditions of the plant are indicated by a number (0 for standard conditions).",
    "The predictability of each motif is indicated by a 'p' followed by several 1 s and 0 s for low and high rates of gene expression, respectively.",
    "The delimiter is followed by the motif number within the metacluster and its orientation (forward or reverse).",
    "Finally, the number of seqlets included, the information content, and the consensus sequences are added at the end of the EPM.",
    "For example, epmArth-S019-p0m06 has a sum importance score of 0.31, a maximum importance score of 0.03 and a minimum score of -0.001 (Supplementary Data 4)."
  ]
}